Problem:

nums = [12,345,2,6,7896]

Output:

2
Core Idea

Count how many numbers have even digit length.

Pattern

Digit Manipulation

Approaches
String Method
count = 0

for num in nums:
    if len(str(num)) % 2 == 0:
        count += 1
Mathematical Method
digits = len(str(num))

or

while num > 0:
    digits += 1
    num //= 10
Time Complexity

O(n)

Key Learning

Convert to string when readability matters.
